title: Science and Engineering Leaders of the Future Fund (SELF)
description: To provide support for travel for an annual trip to Washington D.C. for students in the class The Politics of Space at the CU Boulder.  If the balance reaches $25,000 within five years, the fund will be administered as an endowment.
